description:
Kate and Doree are two moms who discover soothing TikTok videos two years late before they chat with comedian, actress, filmmaker, and podcaster Whitney Cummings! They talk about time budgeting as a form of self-care, why she puts oils on her vagina after every pee, and how her wellness doesn’t have to look like yours.
